     <para>
      修复当主库重启时备库中罕见的断言失败
      （Heikki Linnakangas）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;66235baab">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
Branch: master [7fe312f60] 2025-03-21 11:30:42 -0400
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [1353b1161] 2025-03-21 11:30:42 -0400
