     <para>
      修复 <literal>COPY
      (<replaceable>query</replaceable>) TO ...</literal> 中的断言失败或令人困惑的错误消息，
      当 <replaceable>query</replaceable> 被 <literal>DO
      INSTEAD NOTIFY</literal> 规则重写时（Tender Wang，Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5e94f616c">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Thomas Munro <tmunro@postgresql.org>
Branch: master [98c7c7152] 2024-10-17 22:11:59 +1300
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [4ac5d33a8] 2024-10-17 22:10:29 +1300
